    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts as it should, providing a reliable driving experience. While the exterior paint still retains a nice shine, there are a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all major electronics and climate control systems functioning properly, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. This car is ready for its next owner and would make an excellent daily driver for someone seeking quality and reliability without the price tag of a brand-new model.",
      "price": 34000.0,
